<p>Screw it, storytime. I am so tired of all these terrible threads talking=
 about deniable assets, and the jobs that they pull, which are 90% lies, an=
d 10% shit you looked up on backrub, which are also lies. So now that I am =
out of the game, lets set the record straight about how real operators cond=
