<p>Casting spells does not require a roll, unless otherwise noted. However =
to give orders to anything you control requires a Summoning (Spirit) roll w=
ith a TN equal to the power points invested in that entity. On a success th=
ey carry out the orders to the best of their ability. On a fail they carry =
out the orders to the best of their understanding.</p>
<p>The following are the spells available to be taken:</p>
