<p>Corpses aren=92t summoned by this ability, so there must actually be a s=
upply of bodies in Range. The brain must be intact. An undead Incapacitated=
 by damage can=92t be raised with this power again. Raising non-human targe=
ts does not work, outside of a few edge cases (African Greys, Corvids, Grea=
t Apes), where you can give very limited orders. </p>
<p>They have the following Stat Block:</p>
<p>Attributes: Agility/Strength/Vigor: Same as living - defaults to d6, Sma=
